        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "PLUTO - Play School - Selimpur"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Tanusree Das"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-06-06",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I heard about PLUTO from various sources, especially about this Dhakuria branch of PLUTO located near Selimpur bus stand. My daughter finds it difficult to communicate. After learning about their contributions towards helping in the overall growth and development of kids from one of my friends, I decided to take a trial session by sending my daughter to their Summer Camp. And trust me, she started keeping so happy after joining the Summer Camp, that I finally put her to their Day Care this month onwards. I am very happy at the care taken by the caregivers there. The Teachers at PLUTO, Dhakuria Branch are extremely helpful and approachable. Being a working Professional it becomes really difficult to find a right place that you can call a 2nd abode for your child, but PLUTO is the answer to all those worries and concerns. With the presence and intervention of well trained teachers, their guidance and the scientific model of PLUTO Day Care caters to the needs of my daughter and I am much relieved now. Would love to engage her in more such camps in the near future. I am extremely hopeful that PLUTO shall be able to help my daughter overcome her present challenges and she would experience an all round development out there.Thank you PLUTO for all the support ❤️.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
